urm]] (1874\u20131935)\n* [[Hermann M\u00fcller (Lichtenberg)|Hermann M\u00fcller]] ([[Lichtenberg]]) (1868\u20131932\n* [[Michael Schnabrich]] (1880\u20131939)\n\n==[[German National People's Party]]==\nIn German ''Deutschnationale Volkspartei'', DNVP.\n\n* [[Dirk Agena|Dr. Dirk Agena]]\n* [[Paul Bang|Dr. Paul Bang]]\n* [[Gustav von Bartenwerffer]], [[DNVP]], entered Reichstag 4 April 1930 for Abg. Schiele\n* [[Georg Bachmann]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Wilhelm Bazille]] (1874\u20131934), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Emil Berndt]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Franz Biener]] (1866\u20131940), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Wilhelm Bruhn]] (1869\u20131951), [[DNVP]], left the party October 1929 and became an independent member\n* [[Wilhelm Dingler]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Alwin Domsch]] (Dresden), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Gottfried von Dryander|Dr. Gottfried von Dryander]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Botho-Wendt Graf zu Eulenburg]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Friedrich Everling|Dr. Friedrich Everling]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Axel Freiherr von Freytag-Loringhoven|Dr. Axel Freiherr von Freytag-Loringhoven]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Curt Wilhelm Fromm]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Heinrich Gerns]] (1892\u20131963), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Georg Gottheiner]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Walther Graef]] (Th\u00fcringen), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Gottfried Gok]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Hans von Goldacker]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Heinrich Haag]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Robert Hampe]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Alfred Hanemann|Dr. Alfred Hanemann]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Georg Hartmann (Politiker)|Georg Hartmann]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Johann Jacob Ha\u00dflacher|Dr. Johann Jacob Ha\u00dflacher]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Oskar Hergt]] (1869\u20131967), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Alfred Hugenberg|Dr. Alfred Hugenberg]] (1865\u20131951), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Emil Hemeter]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Willy Jandrey]] (1877\u20131945), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Fritz Kleiner|Dr. Fritz Kleiner]], [[DNVP]], entered Reichstag 2 December 1929 for Abg. Wolf (Oppeln)\n* [[Wilhelm Koch]] (D\u00fcsseldorf), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Albrecht Philipp|Dr. Albrecht Philipp]] (1883\u20131962), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Dietrich Preyer|Dr. Dr. Dietrich Preyer]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Wilhelm Vogt]] (W\u00fcrttemberg), [[DNVP]]\n* [[Max Wallraf]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Kurt Wege (DNVP)|Kurt Wege]], [[DNVP]]\n* [[Kuno von Westarp|Kuno Graf von Westarp]] (1864\u20131945)\n* [[Erich Wienbeck|Dr. Erich Wienbeck]]\n* [[Edgar Wolf]] (Oppeln) resigned 30 November 1929\n* [[Johannes Wolf]] (Stettin)\n* [[Ernst Oberfohren|Dr. Ernst Oberfohren]] (1881\u20131933), [[DNVP]] - party chairman from 12 December 1929 \n* [[Wilhelm Ohler]]\n* [[Reinhold Quaatz|Dr. Reinhold Quaatz]]\n* [[Hans von Troilo]]\n* [[Walther Rademacher|Dr. Walther Rademacher]]\n* [[Jakob Reichert|Dr. Jakob Reichert]]\n* [[Praetorius Freiherr von Richthofen]]\n* [[Carl Rieseberg]]\n* [[Hans Sachs (Reichstagsabgeordneter)|Hans Sachs]] (1874\u20131947), National Liberal Land Party, Guest of the DNVP\n* [[Walter Stubbendorff]]\n* [[Hermann Strathmann|D. Hermann Strathmann]]\n* [[Martin Schiele]] (1870\u20131939), [[DNVP]], resigned 31 March 1930\n* [[Karl Steiniger|Dr. Karl Steiniger]]\n* [[Hermann Staffehl]] (Potsdam)\n* [[Otto Schmidt-Hannover|Otto Schmidt]] (Hannover) (1888\u20131971)\n* [[Otto Schmidt (Stettin)|Otto Schmidt]] (Stettin)\n* [[Hermann Schr\u00f6ter]] (Liegnitz)\n* [[Georg Schultz]] (Bromberg) (1860\u20131945)\n* [[Max Soth]]\n* [[Martin Spahn|Dr. Martin Spahn]] (1875\u20131945)\n* [[Ernst Mentzel]]\n* [[Paula M\u00fcller-Otfried]] (1865\u20131946)\n* [[Wilhelm Laverrenz]] (1879\u20131955)\n* [[Annagrete Lehmann]]\n* [[Bernhard Leopold]]\n* [[Paul von Lettow-Vorbeck]] (1870\u20131964)\n* [[Heinrich Lind]] later independent\n\n===Later formed CNAG===\nThese DNVP members later merged with CNBL to form the Christian National Labor Society (''Christlich-Nationale Arbeitsgemeinschaft'', CNAG).\n\n* [[Emil Hartwig]] (Berlin)\n* [[Otto Hoetzsch|Dr. Otto Hoetzsch]] (1876\u20131946)\n* [[Gottfried Treviranus]] (1891\u20131971)\n* [[Franz Behrens]] (1872\u20131943)\n* [[Gustav H\u00fclser]]\n* [[Wilhelm M\u00f6nke]]\n* [[Reinhard Mumm|D. Reinhard Mumm]] (1873\u20131932)\n* [[Walter von Keudell]] (1884\